column2: SELECT m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1, n.objID, n.distance, p.ra AS ra2, p.dec AS dec2, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMagErr_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMagErr_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMagErr_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMagErr_i, p.modelMag_z, p.modelMagErr_z, psfMag_r, psfMagErr_r, p.cModelMag_r, p.cModelMagErr_r into BOSS_LOWZ-HSC_Gal_Photobj FROM MyDB.BOSS-LOWZ-HSC_RA_DEC AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON n.objID = p.objID
